-- LG Display to Invest $844 Million in LCD Production by 2012, Yonhap Says
-- Kyung Bok Cho
-- 2010-07-27T01:21:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/lg-display-to-invest-844-million-in-lcd-production-by-2012-yonhap-says.html

          
          
             LG Display Co. plans to invest 1
trillion won ($844 million) by 2012 to increase liquid-crystal-
display production in South Korea, Yonhap News reported, citing
the company.  
          
          


  


        